Interface ListContract<E,L extends List<E>>

Type Parameters:
E - The type of the elements.
L - The type of the list.
All Superinterfaces:

public interface ListContract<E,L extends List<E>> extends SequencedCollectionContract<E,L>, ListAddContract<E,L>, ListToArrayContract<E,L>, GetContract<E,L>, SetContract<E,L>, IndexOfContract<E,L>, LastIndexOfContract<E,L>, AddAtPositionContract<E,L>, RemoveAtPositionContract<E,L>, ReplaceAllContract<E,L>, SortContract<E,L>, SubListContract<E,L>
Test suite for classes that implement the List interface. When implementing this class, the only method that will need to be implemented is ProviderSupport.provider().
